<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.5.2">
<l>pēyiṉ mulaiyuṇṭa piḷḷai yivaṉmuṉṉam</l>
<l>māyac cakaṭum marutu miṟuttavaṉ</l>
<l>kāyā malarvaṇṇaṉ kaṇṇaṉ karuṅkuḻal</l>
<l>tūytāka vantukuḻal vārāyak kākkāy</l>
<l rend="indent">tūmaṇivaṇ ṇaṉkuḻal vārāyak kākkāy</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Come so that the curly black hair of Kannan—</l>
<l rend="indent">he who has the colour of the Kaya flower,</l>
<l rend="indent">he who broke the disguised cart and the marutu trees,</l>
<l rend="indent">the child who had previously drank from the breast of the demoness—</l>
<l>is immaculate,</l>
<l>Caw! Caw! Comb [his] curly hair.</l>
<l>Caw! Caw! Comb the curly hair of he with the colour of a pure jewel.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
